still in Engineering, awaiting planning, planned, or released-but-not-
started) and "WIP Units" (productionReleaseStatus === Started, actively
in production). Extracted into a shared UnitListCard component since
both sections render the same row layout.

Item 3: any department can already flag a comment as a delay/blocker
via the existing "Mark as delay / blocker" checkbox on a unit's detail
page (isDelay on UnitComment) - that data existed but was never shown
anywhere outside the unit's own page, so a Director had no way to see
an Assembly supervisor's "this is stuck because X" note without opening
every unit individually. directorSummary() (previous commit) now
includes each unit's most recent delay comment; both Upcoming and WIP
rows show it inline with an amber warning icon when present.
